name: The Brown House "bigcartel" Policies and Procedure-"The Fine Print"
description:
Thanks for Visiting Our "bigcartel" Site, Where Inventory Is Offered For Purchase. 

I Want Everyone to Be Absolutely  Satisfied with Any Item That They May Purchase. As You Know, Almost all Antiques are Characterized by a few Imperfections. My Five Image Limit to the Depiction of Each Piece Makes It Difficult to Demonstrate Every Surface in Close-up. However, as I want You to be pleased with your purchase , I would very  happily send any further photos and descriptions if you should Inquire. I will try my best to offer the most complete worded details as possible.  

If you are not Satisfied with your Purchase I will Gladly refund the Purchase price upon safe return of the same purchased item. I Promise to  pack carefully and include insurance with the shipping price. At this time, I do not plan to charge for any packing materials and handling. If an item is returned because it did not match the description, I do not refund the shipping, handling and insurance. 

At this time, I am going to ship at a fixed rate of 15.00 per item with any added items shipped with the first item for 1.00.  If the shipping, handling and insurance is greater than 15.00 for the first item, I will Absorb the cost. If it cost Me less than 15.00, I promise to refund the difference to you through Paypal.

I ship once a week, on Saturdays.

If You Are Interested in Shipping to Other than the Lower 48 States, Please Contact Us So We Can Render An Exact Shipping Quote for Any One or More Items.

Thanks for Visiting our Store!  Charles
